To compile the software, do the following:

ln -sf configure/configure.nwp-libs.<platform> configure.nwp-libs
make

If successful, all module and library files will be placed in
./include and ./lib, respectively.

!!!! FOR LINUX MACHINES WITH LMOD CAPABILITIES !!!!

Benearth ./tools, there exists example module template files for
(currently) supportted NOAA RDHPCS machines; please consult the
notes/documentation within.

!!!! IMPORTANT !!!!

Currently, only a generic Darwin OSX platform and the NOAA RDHPCS Jet
and Theia machines are supported.